==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Automatism
<hw>Au*tom"a*tism</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or
quality of being automatic; the power of self-moving; automatic,
mechanical, or involuntary action.</def> <specif>Specifically:</specif>
<fld>(Metaph.)</fld> <def>A theory as to the activity of
matter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>automatize</ent>⟦br⟧
